{
  "id": "adv_main_03_13_02",
  "title": "BIG4編1章62話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_live-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-host.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-host001.m4a",
      "text": "ついに因縁の戦いが始まります！　あらゆるアイドルを\nなぎ倒し、我が道を進み続けるBIG4・どりきゅん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And now‚ the fateful battle begins! Crushing all idols in their path‚\nthe BIG4 DoriKyun continues to advance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.8098867416
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-host.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-host002.m4a",
      "text": "そして、二度の敗戦を経てなおも立ち上がり\n今宵三度目の戦いに挑む――月のテンペスト！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And rising up once more despite experiencing two defeats\ntonight‚ they challenge their third battle――Moon Tempest!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8023.446591700001,
          "startTime": 18.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.9637638728
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-lmn001.m4a",
      "text": "あれだけ無様な姿を晒しておいて\nよくまたこの舞台に戻って来る気になれたわねぇ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After showing such a pathetic display\nyou still have the nerve to return to this stage?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.258321762
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "私達五人とも、今日の再戦を楽しみにしていました\n今度こそ――私達が勝ちます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All five of us have been looking forward to this rematch today‚\nThis time――we will win‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.471567869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.9115186054
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-lim001.m4a",
      "text": "はっ。言うようになったじゃねぇか\n随分とふてぶてしい面をするようになったな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ha‚ You've gotten bolder‚ haven't you?\nYou've got quite the impudent look on your face‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.3972784995
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-lmn002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃……それに他の子達も\nこの前戦った時とは、目の色が変わってるじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚‚‚ and the other girls too‚\nyour eyes are different from when we last fought‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.9042850493
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_rival-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 51.90429
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-lmn003.m4a",
      "text": "舞台に上がるまでは半信半疑だったけど\n何か……あなた達の中で変化でもあったみたいねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was half in doubt until you stepped on stage‚ but\nit seems like‚‚‚ something changed within you‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3395961807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.2224934894
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-lim002.m4a",
      "text": "想いだのなんだの、どうせ口だけかと思ってたが……\nとびきり楽しめそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought all that about \"thoughts\" and whatnot was just talk‚‚‚\nbut this looks like it'll be a blast‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "（れもんさんと来夢さんも……今までと雰囲気が違う）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Lemon-san and Lime-san too‚‚‚ their atmosphere is different than before‚）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.027482128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.027482128
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.8220854758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "（そうか、私達は……）\n（一度目の戦いの時も、二度目の戦いの時も……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（So‚ we‚‚‚）\n（During the first battle‚ and the second battle‚‚‚）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.0346
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "（本当の意味で、あの人達と同じステージには）\n（立っていなかったんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（We weren't truly‚‚‚）\n（Standing on the same stage as them‚）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.1633092243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "（どんな相手でも、手は抜かない二人だけど……）\n（それでも、今日は……明らかに気迫が違う）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Although those two never hold back against any opponent‚‚‚）\n（Even so‚ today‚‚‚ their fighting spirit is clearly different‚）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.6873895008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.6873895008
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.3247383117
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-lim003.m4a",
      "text": "お前の言ってた「本当の強さ」とやらを見せてみろよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Show me this \"true strength\" you were talking about‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.3247383117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.0158263842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです。その上で……\nこのステージをしっかり盛り上げてみせますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ And on top of that‚‚‚\nwe'll make sure to really heat up this stage‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "私達が……月ストが、どりきゅんに勝つことで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By us‚‚‚ by Moon Tempest defeating DoriKyun‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.7397037188,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4626.962947899998,
          "startTime": 111.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.7397037188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-lmn004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、盛り上げ方が分かってきたじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ you've learned how to hype up the crowd‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1858263015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.1858263015
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 115.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-lmn005.m4a",
      "text": "今の言葉が強がりに見えない辺り\nとっても生意気に成長したみたいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fact that those words don't sound like bravado\nmeans you've grown quite impudent‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.1217441558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-lim004.m4a",
      "text": "いいぜ。あたしとれもん、そしてお前らの本気の戦いだ\n使えるものは全部使って挑んでこい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good‚ This is a real fight between me and Lemon‚ and you guys‚\nUse everything you've got and come at us‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.4628783226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ……もちろんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚‚‚ Of course‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.4628783226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "big4challengestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.9747603178
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 136.1748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-host.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_13_02-host003.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、抽選の結果が出ました\n因縁の対決の先攻は～……どりきゅん！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And now‚ the results of the lottery are in!\nThe first to perform in this fateful confrontation is~‚‚‚ DoriKyun!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6791.905840200002,
          "startTime": 143.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
